title: Andis Micro Turbo 1600 Watt Dual Voltage Hair Dryer - White (33805)
description: Andis 33805 Micro Turbo 1600 Watt Dryer has dual voltage for worldwide travel.  There are two heat, air settings and a quiet fan and motor. It features Lifeline shock protection.
